Dialogue.Value: GREAT WORK!,I’M SURE THE MISTRESS,WOULD HAVE LOVED IT!
I DON’T REALLY DO MUCH,FOR THIS PERFORMANCE....
BUT WITHOUT ME，THE,WHOLE THING WOULD JUST,SOUND WRONG!
I THINK THE MISTRESS WAS,PLANNING ON ADDING,MORE TO THIS TUNE!
BUT BACK THEN，SHE WAS,TOO SMALL TO REACH ALL,THE KEYS!
MAYBE SHE PLANNED ON,HAVING A FAMILY MEMBER,PLAY THESE NOTES?
THEY SAY IT TAKES 10000,HOURS TO BECOME AN,EXPERT AT ANYTHING!
SO IF WE’VE REHEARSED,THIS RECORDED SEQUENCE,EVERY DAY....
DOES THIS MEAN WE CAN,CALL OURSELVES EXPERT,PIANISTS?
I DON’T THINK MISTRESS,REMILIA IS COMING BACK....
NO，NO，HAPPY THOUGHTS，,HAPPY THOUGHTS....!,FOCUS ON THE MUSIC!
